snippet.title: Dust: An Elysian Tail - Steam Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Dust: An Elysian Tail, a side-scrolling action-RPG created by Dean Dodrill with music by HyperDuck SoundWorks, is now available on Steam!

Get it now! http://store.steampowered.com/app/236090/
